casebody.data:
Cincinnati Bar Association v. Wilson.

[Cite as Cincinnati Bar Assn. v. Wilson (1992), 65 Ohio St.3d 296.]

(No. 91-1771 — Submitted October 13, 1992 — Decided December 14, 1992.) *297Beth Silverman and Peter Rosenwald, for relator. W David Bertsche, Jr., for respondent. Per Curiam.

We agree with the findings and recommendation of the board. We hereby publicly reprimand respondent and tax costs to her.

Judgment accordingly.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
